OL,6,FPolice officers used reasonable force
OL,7,Fto restrain a 23-year-old man who
OL,8,Flater died in hospital, an independent
OL,9,Fwatchdog has found.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct (IOPC) found no evidence that
OL,13,Fofficers "caused or contributed" to
OL,14,Fthe death of 23-year-old Chad Allford
OL,15,Fin Alfreton in October 2021.
OL,17,FIt did, however, confirm the three
OL,18,Fpolice constables did not activate
OL,19,Ftheir body worn cameras prior to
OL,20,Fentering the property.
