OL,3,CPolice officers used reasonable force
OL,4,Cto restrain 23-year-old who later died
OL,6,FAfter an inquest at Chesterfield,
OL,7,Fwhich ended on Thursday, a jury
OL,8,Fconcluded Mr Allford died by
OL,9,Fmisadventure after deliberately
OL,10,Fplacing cocaine in his mouth, which
OL,11,Fhad unintentionally led to his death.
OL,13,FAfter his death, Derbyshire Police
OL,14,Freferred itself to the police watchdog.
OL,16,FAccording to the IOPC, footage from
OL,17,Fbody-worn cameras showed Chad Allford
OL,18,Fputting a "white powder into his
OL,19,Fmouth, believed to be cocaine".
