OL,3,CPolice officers used reasonable force
OL,4,Cto restrain 23-year-old who later died
OL,6,FThey say the officers used reasonable
OL,7,Fforce trying to stop Mr Allford from
OL,8,Fswallowing the powder.
OL,10,FAccording to Derbyshire Constabulary,
OL,11,FMr Alford became seriously unwell when
OL,12,Fhe was detained. An ambulance was
OL,13,Fcalled, and CPR was carried out, but
OL,14,Fhe later died in hospital.
OL,16,FThe IOPC did find the three officers
OL,17,Frestraining Mr Allford had not turned
OL,18,Fon their body cams.
