OL,3,CPolice officers used reasonable force
OL,4,Cto restrain 23-year-old who later died
OL,6,FThey also found that a sergeant had
OL,7,Fperformed a stop and search on
OL,8,Fsomeone, taking keys to Mr Alford's
OL,9,Fhome in the process, without fully
OL,10,Fexplaining their rights.
OL,12,FThe IOPC said these failures of
OL,13,Fpractice "could be addressed through
OL,14,Fthe reflective practice review
OL,15,Fprocess.".
OL,17,FIOPC Regional Director Derrick
OL,18,FCampbell said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,19,Fwith Mr Allford's family and all of
OL,20,Fthose affected by his tragic death.
